Package: viscover
Title: Overlay and visualize Soil Data Layer and Cropland Data Layer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Xiaodan", "Lyu", email = "lyux1994@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package embed a shiny app to visualize soil survey data and cropland data layer. Some functions to fetch CDL file and values are also provided.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
